description: The GraphCode represents the scene where Maria is swimming in her pool. 'Maria' is defined as an object (type 1), 'swim' is defined as an activity (type 9), and 'pool' is defined as an object (type 1). The relationship between 'Maria' and 'swim' is 'perform' (type 8), and the relationship between 'swim' and 'pool' is 'in' (type 7).
